OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools given new guidance 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon stopping phone use      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools in England have been given new 
OL,6, guidance intended to stop the use of   
OL,7, mobile phones during the school day.   
OL,9,FThe government said the move was part  
OL,10,Fof a plan to "minimise disruption and  
OL,11,Fimprove behaviour in classrooms".      
OL,13,FIt added that many schools had already 
OL,14,Fbanned phones and the change would     
OL,15,Fensure a consistent approach.          
OL,17,FBut one school leaders union said the  
OL,18,Fmost compulsive use of phones happened 
OL,19,Fout of school and called the change a  
OL,20,F"non-policy for a non-problem".        
